features: 【6 Pack Face Masks Skincare】Each of our face mask are made with nature extract offering a variety of care options for your skin. Brightening, deep cleaning, moisturizing, rejuvenating, repairing, soothing. Meet your daily needs for hydrating and moisturizing.

【Hydrated Skin & Rich Essence】The premium natural adult/girls skin care perfectly covers by curved area on face and make the skin evenly absorb the essence. The face masks beauty brighten and hydrate the skin with Hyaluronic Acid and Multivitamin Essence.They are moderate thickness and not easily deformed. Gold proportion essence are non-sticky and instantly hydrates and refreshes.

【Intensive Solution】Our sheet mask helps you choose the best one for your unique complexion out of six different masks. You can apply on your neck or body with an ample amount of nutrient-rich, high concentration essence.

【Daily Use】Our korean face mask is gentle enough for daily use and easy to apply and remove. They mold to the contours of your face, ensuring every inch of your skin benefits from the nourishing formula.

【Suitable for all skin types】 This face mask set is not only suitable for women, but also for teenagers. We can build a skin barrier as early as possible to improve the quality of facial skin and keep the skin moist, soft and shiny. The formula is light and gentle, and is suitable for all skin types, including oily, dry and mixed skin. (Note: Please do a post-ear test for sensitive skin before using it.)
description: Product description Skin problems often occur, often caused by lack of water. Recommend this moisturizing mask set-inspired by nature, designed to create moist, smooth and luminous skin!
